se.hig.exte.repository

Interface SettingsRepository

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<Settings,java.lang.Integer>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<Settings,java.lang.Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<Settings,java.lang.Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<Settings>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<Settings,java.lang.Integer>

    @Repository
public interface SettingsRepository
extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<Settings,java.lang.Integer>
    An interface used for database operations on Settings objects. References to this interface are automatically given an implementation by Spring Boot when using the Autowired annotation.
